en-us:
1. You will be able to withdraw money when the accumulated amount reaches R$100\n
2. Inviting friends to register on 2048bet.COM will help you withdraw money quickly. For each friend who successfully registers, you will get 1 drawing opportunity.\n
4. Each user's activity is valid for 3 days. If no withdrawal is made within 3 days, the funds will be lost.\n
5. The winnings will be added to your wallet and you can play for free and win more real money or withdraw it directly.\n
6. All illegal means of obtaining bonuses will not be recognized, including but not limited to account swiping on the same IP and the same device. We will eliminate the bonuses obtained by said accounts. The final interpretation right of this activity belongs to 2048bet. COM
